@startuml
title Flutter + Dart 知识图谱学习系统框架图（v3）

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Microsoft YaHei
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #444444
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.2
skinparam package {
  BorderColor #6C8EF5
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFF
  RoundCorner 18
}
skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #6C8EF5
  BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  RoundCorner 14
}
skinparam database {
  BorderColor #666666
  BackgroundColor #FCFCFC
}

actor 学生 as Student
actor 教师 as Teacher
actor 管理员 as Admin

package "Flutter UI" as UI {
  [LoginPage\n登录入口]
  [HomePage\n导航中心]
  [GraphListPage\n图谱列表]
  [GraphDetailPage\n图谱详情与节点交互]
  [DocumentListPage\nPPT / PDF 资料]
  [VideoListPage\n视频资源]
  [QuizPage\n章节测验]
  [ProgressPage\n学习进度]
  [FavoritesPage\n收藏内容]
  [LearningPlanPage\n学习计划]
  [SettingsPage\n设置]
  [SearchPage\n搜索]
}

package "Application Service / DAO" as APP {
  [AuthService]
  [GraphDao]
  [QuizDao]
  [FavoriteDao]
  [LearningRecordDao]
  [UserDao]
  [DatabaseHelper]
}

package "Dart Data Model" as MODEL {
  [GraphModel]
  [NodeModel]
  [EdgeModel]
  [QuestionModel]
  [QuizResultModel]
  [UserModel]
}

database "SQLite\nassets/learning_data.db" as DB

Student --> [LoginPage]
Teacher --> [LoginPage]
Admin --> [LoginPage]

[LoginPage] --> [AuthService]
[AuthService] --> [UserDao]
[UserDao] --> [DatabaseHelper]

[HomePage] --> [GraphListPage]
[HomePage] --> [QuizPage]
[HomePage] --> [VideoListPage]
[HomePage] --> [DocumentListPage]
[HomePage] --> [ProgressPage]
[HomePage] --> [LearningPlanPage]
[HomePage] --> [FavoritesPage]
[HomePage] --> [SettingsPage]
[HomePage] --> [SearchPage]

[GraphListPage] --> [GraphDao]
[GraphDetailPage] --> [GraphDao]
[GraphDetailPage] --> [FavoriteDao]
[GraphDetailPage] --> [LearningRecordDao]

[QuizPage] --> [QuizDao]
[ProgressPage] --> [QuizDao]
[ProgressPage] --> [LearningRecordDao]
[FavoritesPage] --> [FavoriteDao]

[GraphDao] --> [DatabaseHelper]
[QuizDao] --> [DatabaseHelper]
[FavoriteDao] --> [DatabaseHelper]
[LearningRecordDao] --> [DatabaseHelper]
[DatabaseHelper] --> DB

[GraphDao] ..> [GraphModel]
[GraphDao] ..> [NodeModel]
[GraphDao] ..> [EdgeModel]
[QuizDao] ..> [QuestionModel]
[QuizDao] ..> [QuizResultModel]
[UserDao] ..> [UserModel]

note right of UI
Flutter 负责页面渲染、导航与交互：
1. MaterialApp 启动应用
2. HomePage 提供底部导航
3. 图谱、资料、视频、测验、进度等页面
   构成完整学习闭环
end note

note right of APP
Dart 业务层负责：
1. 登录状态管理
2. 图谱、测验、收藏、学习记录访问
3. 封装本地 SQLite 读写逻辑
end note

note bottom of DB
本地数据库保存：
- 图谱数据 graphs / nodes / edges
- 题库与测验结果
- 收藏与学习记录
- 用户与当前会话信息
end note

@enduml
